data.description: Nestled in the heart of Pickerington, this enchanting two-story home is a perfect blend of  comfort and classic charm. Boasting a new roof installed in 2019 and new windows added in 2020, this residence stands as a testament to both style and structural integrity. The 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths offer a spacious and versatile living space for families or individuals seeking a cozy haven. The tastefully designed interior features a seamless flow between the living room, kitchen, and dining areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings. With its meticulously maintained exterior, this home is a true gem, providing a perfect retreat.
